# Cloudflare Pages redirects.
# Note: www -> apex is NOT redirected here. Pages _redirects cannot match on
# hostname (www and the apex share this one file), so www serves the site with a
# canonical tag pointing to the apex (Google de-dups it). A hard 301 needs a
# zone-level Redirect Rule (Rules -> Redirect Rules -> "Redirect WWW to Root").

# Friendly aliases -> canonical pages.
/models               /can-i-run            301
/devices              /best-llm-for         301
/model                /can-i-run            301
/llms-full            /llms-full.txt        301
/llms                 /llms.txt             301
